reviewText: SUPERB HITS OF THE BEST FILMS OF 1950S IS A REAL TREAT TO ENJOY FROM THE GIFTED SINGERS AND THE TALENTED ACTORS. A MUST PART OF ANY ONE'S COLLECTION.

High quality audio and video. I would love the get more items from this supplier. The one problem I face is that the list of songs are not always available. I am interested in volume -1 of the best of 1950 and volume-2 of the best of 1960 in Audio CD's and Video DVD.
